referral_conversion_time.label: referral_conversion_time
referral_conversion_time.query: dataset = load "${App.Datasets.HLS_Referral8_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; a = group dataset by all; a = foreach a generate avg('Lead_Age_Days') as 'avg_Lead_Age_Days', case when avg('Lead_Age_Days') < {{coalesce(cell(referral_age_all.result, 0, "avg_Lead_Age_Days"),0).asString()}} then "This Referral (on track)" else "This Referral (behind)" end as 'ReferralType', 1 as 'order'; dataset = filter dataset by 'IsConverted' == "true"; b = filter dataset by 'HealthCloudGA_Specialty__c' == "Cardiology"; b = group b by all; b = foreach b generate avg('Lead_Age_Days') as 'avg_Lead_Age_Days', "Avg Specialty" as 'ReferralType', 2 as 'order'; c = filter dataset by 'HealthCloudGA_TypeOfService__c' == "Surgery"; c = group c by all; c = foreach c generate avg('Lead_Age_Days') as 'avg_Lead_Age_Days', "Avg Type of Service" as 'ReferralType', 3 as 'order'; d = filter dataset by 'HealthCloudGA_InsuranceType__c' == "Medicare"; d = group d by all; d = foreach d generate avg('Lead_Age_Days') as 'avg_Lead_Age_Days', "Avg Insurance Type" as 'ReferralType', 4 as 'order'; e = group dataset by all; e = foreach e generate avg('Lead_Age_Days') as 'avg_Lead_Age_Days', "Avg Overall" as 'ReferralType', 5 as 'order'; f = union a,b,c,d,e; f = order f by 'order' asc;

description_text.label: description_text
description_text.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.HLS_Referral8_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate count() as 'count', case when first('IsConverted') == "true" then "This referral converted in {{coalesce(cell(referral_age.result, 0, "avg_Lead_Age_Days"),"0").asString()}} days. The average time for converting a referral is {{coalesce(cell(referral_age_all.result, 0, "avg_Lead_Age_Days"),"0").asString()}} days." else "This referral has not converted and has been open for {{coalesce(cell(referral_age.result, 0, "avg_Lead_Age_Days"),"0").asString()}} days. The average time for converting a referral is {{coalesce(cell(referral_age_all.result, 0, "avg_Lead_Age_Days"),"0").asString()}} days." end as 'description_text';
